# Frontend Env Template Index
#
# Frontend env is browser-facing. Only `VITE_*` keys belong here.
# Never put DB credentials, LLM provider keys, or backend secrets in frontend env.
#
# Local Vite-only development:
#   cp frontend/.env.local.example frontend/.env.local
#
# Production/static frontend deployment:
#   Use frontend/.env.prod.example as the platform/build-time reference.
